Configuration
-------------

Before the tests can be run, you need to:

 * install pytest package (pip install pytest)
 * create settings.py file in this directory,
    - copy settings.py-example to settings.py
    - make sure settings.py contains correct credentials


Running tests
-------------

Use 'pytest' command to run tests. Example:

 # run all tests
 $ pytest

 # run all tests in unit/ directory
 $ pytest unit/

 # run one specific test
 pytest unit/test_db.py::TestModel::test_del_with_default_pos

